The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization algorithms (cs.AI), as well as the design and analysis of algorithms (cs.DS). The concept of social efficiency is related to economics and market design (cs.EC), and the paper also discusses information theory (cs.IT) in the context of Bayesian mechanisms.
